```
SimpleCompiler compiler = new SimpleCompiler();
Class&lt;?&gt; fooCls = compiler.compile(&quot;Foo&quot;, &quot;class Foo {}&quot;);
// later...
Class&lt;?&gt; barCls = compiler.compile(&quot;Bar&quot;, &quot;class Bar { /* use Foo...*/ }&quot;);
```

